<h1>Articles</h1>

<h2>Our blog has <%= Article.count_without_status('archived') %> articles and counting!</h2>
<%= link_to "Create a new article!", new_article_path %>
<h3>Blog current public articles:</h3>
<%= render 'articles/articles_list', articles: @articles, filter: :public %>

<h3>Blog archived articles:</h3>
<%= render 'articles/articles_list', articles: @articles, filter: :archived %>



